longBusinessSummary: Hi Ho Silver Resources Inc., a mineral exploration company, explores for and develops mineral properties in Canada. The company holds a 100% interest in the Illite Clay- Kootenay Clay project; and an option to acquire a 100% interest in the Fairview South Okanagan property located in British Columbia. It also has interests in the Isle silver property that consists of 6 units totaling 123.97 hectares located northwest of Kaslo, British Columbia; and Tatler silver property comprising 22 units totaling 452.97 hectares situated to the southwest of Invermere, British Columbia. The company was founded in 2005 and is headquartered in Maple Ridge, Canada.
